Mogol, cerrado na estrada para o rio Ventania, ca. 16°32'S-42°49'W, ca. 900 m alt., 5 Nov 1990 (fl.), 
<emphasis id="73BDA67D0C78D9B00C40DF62CC399EFF" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="137">J. R. Pirani CFCR13358</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="9AB336FADBC89094538E84B8107538F8" bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="137">Holotype</emphasis>
: SPF barcode SPF 69503!; 
<emphasis id="3C3C894C3F2349247C5598653FADA79B" bold="true" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="137">isotypes</emphasis>
